caller_intent: Vicky Hill requested the Travelers insurance phone number and a copy of her declaration page for a new job, though she did not have her policy number on hand.
resolution_steps: Agent provided Travelers' customer service phone number (877-824-6824) after confirming Vicky's identity.
Agent asked for Vicky's policy number but she admitted she did not have it.
Agent offered to send a copy of the declaration page via email after confirming Vicky's email address (vickiekayee317@gmail.com).
Agent estimated a 20-minute processing time for the document request, which Vicky agreed to.
summary: Vicky Hill requested Travelers insurance contact information and a declaration page for a new job. The agent provided the phone number, offered to send the declaration page via email after verifying Vicky's email address, and estimated a 20-minute processing time. The call concluded with Vicky agreeing to wait for the document.
